         <abstract id="aspace_bfe68fa1f71bed3ab48013991c6540a5">Yale University celebrated its 275th anniversary on 15 October 1976. The records primarily consist of background materials, drafts and transcripts of ceremonial remarks, and writings by invited speakers, including a commemorative poem by Archibald Macleish.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_de5c1fcddf3706aabbc9dcd88a7ff09a">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 2-A (YRG 2-A), Records of the President.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_2fd3f7c3e179c243f8b632882c3d2627">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of the President, May 1977.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_2980b31cdf929e326cf62e80fd5d5bfc">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_80a04ef71ffb6f536f9144fe79512fa6">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>275th Anniversary Commemoration, Yale University, Records (YRU 15). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_d6fa10f071c892d30ec9344dc786fd44">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically by subject, name, or form of material.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_9e0484d3766a83417a5c13b695393bc3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Yale University celebrated its 275th anniversary on 15 October 1976. The records primarily consist of background materials, drafts and transcripts of ceremonial remarks, and writings by invited speakers, including a commemorative poem by Archibald Macleish.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
